---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<I=k>
Dataset 

  app.activeDocument.dataSets[index  

Description

A set of data used for dynamic publishing. A dataset allows you to collect a number of variables and
their dynamic data into one object. You must have at least one variable bound to an art item in order to
create a dataset. See the class <L=2i#h> Variable </L> .

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Properties 

Dataset.name 

  app.activeDocument.dataSets[index].name  

Description

Then name of the dataset.

Type

String.

