<I=1i>
Document.convertCoordinate() 

  app.activeDocument.convertCoordinate(coordinate,   source,   destination)  

Description

Converts the given point between artboard and document coordinate systems. Returns the converted point
coordinates.

Parameters

+----------------+------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
| Parameter      | Type                                                 | Description                  |
+================+======================================================+==============================+
|   coordinate   | Point                                                | Point to convert             |
+----------------+------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
|   source       | <L=2o#4A> CoordinateSystem </L>                      | Source coordinate system     |
+----------------+------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+
|                | <L=2o#4A> CoordinateSystem </L>                      | Destination coordinate       |
|  destination   |                                                      | system                       |
+----------------+------------------------------------------------------+------------------------------+

Returns

Point.

