<I=1j><I=4S>
Document.exportFile() 

  app.activeDocument.exportFile(exportFile,   exportFormat   [,options])  

Description

Exports the document to the specified file using one of the predefined export file formats. The
appropriate file extension is automatically appended to the file name, except for Photoshop® documents.
For these, you must include the file extension (PSD) in the file specification.

Parameters

+---------------------+---------------------------------------------------------+-----------------------+
| Parameter           | Type                                                    | Description           |
+=====================+=========================================================+=======================+
|   exportFile        | File                                                    | File to save          |
+---------------------+---------------------------------------------------------+-----------------------+
|   exportFormat      | <L=2o#4O> ExportType </L>                               | Export file format    |
+---------------------+---------------------------------------------------------+-----------------------+
|   options           | <L=2i#h> Variable </L> , optional                       | todo                  |
+---------------------+---------------------------------------------------------+-----------------------+

Returns

Nothing.

