DocumentPreset.artboardRowsOrCols 

  documentPreset.artboardRowsOrCols  

Description

The number of rows (for rows layout) or columns (for column layout) of artboards. Range: 1 to (
  numArtboards   - 1) or 1 for single row or column layouts. Default: 1

