ExportOptionsAutoCAD.exportOption 

  exportOptionsAutoCAD.exportOption  

Description

Specifies whether to preserve appearance or editability during export.

Default:   AutoCADExportOption.MaximizeEditability   .

Type

<L=2o#4e> AutoCADExportOption </L>

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
