---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

GradientColor 

  gradientColor  

Description

A gradient color specification in a Gradient object. A script can create a new gradient color using a
reference to an existing gradient in the document. If no existing gradient object is referenced, a
default gradient is supplied.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Properties 

GradientColor.angle 

  gradientColor.angle  

Description

The gradient vector angle in degrees. Default: 0.0.

Type

Number (double).

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<I=1>
