<I=B>
GraphItem.translate() 

```javascript
app.activeDocument.graphItems[index].translate([deltaX] [,deltaY]
  [,transformObjects] [,transformFillPatterns]
  [,transformFillGradients] [,transformStrokePatterns]
)
```

Description

Repositions the art item relative to the current position, where   deltaX   is the horizontal offset and
  deltaY   is the vertical offset.

Parameters

+-------------------------------+-----------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
| Parameter                     | Type                        | Description                             |
+===============================+=============================+=========================================+
