<I=1l>
LegacyTextItem 

  legacyTextItems[index  

Description

A text object created in Illustrator CS (version 10) or earlier, which is uneditable until converted. To
convert legacy text, see <L=Y#n> LegacyTextItems.convertToNative() </L> .

You can view, move, and print legacy text, but you cant edit it. Legacy text has an “x” through its
bounding box when selected.

