Example 

Example name 

```javascript
// Locks all mesh items in the current document
if (app.documents.length > 0) {
  var doc = app.activeDocument;
  for (var i = 0; i < doc.meshItems.length; i++) {
    doc.meshItems[i].locked = true;
  }
}
```
