---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<I=1x>
PlacedItem 

  app.activeDocument.placedItems[index  

Description

An artwork item placed in a document as a linked file.

For example, an artwork object created using the   File   >   Place   command in Illustrator or using the
  add()   method of the   placedItems   collection object is a placed item.

For information, see <L=1v#j> PlacedItems </L> .

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

