PlacedItem.resize() 

  app.activeDocument.placedItems[index].resize(scaleX,   scaleY[,changePositions][,changeFillPatterns][,changeFillGradients][,changeStrokePattern][,changeLineWidths][,scaleAbout])  

Description

Scales the art item where   scaleX   is the horizontal scaling factor and   scaleY   is the vertical
scaling factor. 100.0 = 100%.

Parameters

+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
| Parameter      | Type                                       | Description                             |
+================+============================================+=========================================+
|   scaleX       | Number (double)                            | Horizontal scaling factor               |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   scaleY       | Number (double)                            | Vertical scaling factor                 |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   cha          | Boolean, optional                          | Whether to effect art object positions  |
| ngePositions   |                                            | and orientations                        |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   change       | Boolean, optional                          | Whether to transform fill patterns      |
| FillPatterns   |                                            |                                         |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   changeF      | Boolean, optional                          | Whether to transform fill gradients     |
| illGradients   |                                            |                                         |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   changeS      | Boolean, optional                          | Whether to transform stroke patterns    |
| trokePattern   |                                            |                                         |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   chan         | Number (double), optional                  | The amount to scale line widths         |
| geLineWidths   |                                            |                                         |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   scaleAbout   | <L=2o#62> Transformation </L> , optional   | The point to use as anchor, to          |
|                |                                            | transform about                         |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+

Returns

Nothing.

