---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<I=z>
PluginItem.resize() 

  app.activeDocument.pluginItems[index].resize(scaleX,   scaleY[,changePositions][,changeFillPatterns][,changeFillGradients][,changeStrokePattern][,changeLineWidths][,scaleAbout])  

Description

Scales the art item where   scaleX   is the horizontal scaling factor and   scaleY   is the vertical
scaling factor. 100.0 = 100%.

Parameters

+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
| Parameter      | Type                                       | Description                             |
+================+============================================+=========================================+
|   scaleX       | Number (double)                            | Horizontal scaling factor               |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   scaleY       | Number (double)                            | Vertical scaling factor                 |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   cha          | Boolean, optional                          | Whether to effect art object positions  |
| ngePositions   |                                            | and orientations                        |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   change       | Boolean, optional                          | Whether to transform fill patterns      |
| FillPatterns   |                                            |                                         |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   changeF      | Boolean, optional                          | Whether to transform fill gradients     |
| illGradients   |                                            |                                         |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   changeS      | Boolean, optional                          | Whether to transform stroke patterns    |
| trokePattern   |                                            |                                         |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   chan         | Number (double), optional                  | The amount to scale line widths         |
| geLineWidths   |                                            |                                         |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   scaleAbout   | <L=2o#62> Transformation </L> , optional   | The point to use as anchor, to          |
|                |                                            | transform about                         |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+

Returns

Nothing.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<I=A>
PluginItem.rotate() 

  app.activeDocument.pluginItems[index].rotate(angle[,changePositions][,changeFillPatterns][,changeFillGradients][,changeStrokePattern][,rotateAbout])  

Description

Rotates the art item relative to the current rotation.

The object is rotated counter-clockwise if the   angle   value is positive, clockwise if the value is
negative.

Parameters

+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
| Parameter      | Type                                       | Description                             |
+================+============================================+=========================================+
|   angle        | Number (double)                            | The angle amount to rotate the element  |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   cha          | Boolean, optional                          | Whether to effect art object positions  |
| ngePositions   |                                            | and orientations                        |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   change       | Boolean, optional                          | Whether to transform fill patterns      |
| FillPatterns   |                                            |                                         |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   changeF      | Boolean, optional                          | Whether to transform fill gradients     |
| illGradients   |                                            |                                         |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|   changeS      | Boolean, optional                          | Whether to transform stroke patterns    |
| trokePattern   |                                            |                                         |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+
|                | <L=2o#62> Transformation </L> , optional   | The point to use as anchor, to          |
|  rotateAbout   |                                            | transform about                         |
+----------------+--------------------------------------------+-----------------------------------------+

Returns

Nothing.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
