---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<I=1L>
RasterItem 

  app.activeDocument.rasterItems[index  

Description

A bitmap art item in a document. A script can create a raster item from an external file, or by copying
an existing raster item with the   duplicate   method.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Properties 

RasterItem.artworkKnockout 

