RasterItem.trace() 

  app.activeDocument.rasterItems[index].trace()  

Description

Converts the raster art for this object to vector art, using default options.

Reorders the raster art into the source art of a plug-in group, and converts it into a group of filled
and/or stroked paths that resemble the original image.

Creates and returns a <L=1w#1o> PluginItem </L> object that references a <L=2g#r> TracingObject </L>
object.

