<I=f>
Symbol 

  app.activeDocument.symbols[index  

Description

An art item that is stored in the Symbols palette, and can be reused one or more times in the document
without duplicating the art data. Symbols are contained in documents.

Instances of   Symbol   in a document are associated with <L=23#1j> SymbolItem </L> objects, which store
the art object properties.

