SymbolItem 

  app.activeDocument.symbolItems[index  

Description

An art item made reusable by adding it to the Symbols palette.

A   SymbolItem   is linked to the <L=22#f> Symbol </L> from which it was created and changes if you
modify the associated   Symbol   object.

