|   ArtClippingOption.OUTPUTARTBOARDBOUNDS           | Output size is the size of the artboard.         |
+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------+
|   ArtClippingOption.OUTPUTCROPRECTBOUNDS           | Output size is the size of the crop area.        |
+----------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------+

