Creating paths and shapes

-   <L=2x#4>Paths</L>
    -   <L=2x#1>Specifying a series of x-y coordinates</L>
    -   <L=2x#2>Using path point objects</L>
    -   <L=2x#3>Combining path point types</L>
-   <L=2x#8>Shapes</L>
