Creating paths and shapes

-   <L=2D#4>Paths</L>
    -   <L=2D#1>Specifying a series of x-y coordinates</L>
    -   <L=2D#2>Using path point objects</L>
    -   <L=2D#3>Combining path point types</L>
-   <L=2D#7>Shapes</L>
