Launching and quitting Illustrator from a script

-   <L=2R#4>Launching and activating Illustrator</L>
    -   <L=2R#1>AppleScript</L>
    -   <L=2R#2>JavaScript</L>
    -   <L=2R#3>VBScript</L>
-   <L=2R#8>Quitting Illustrator</L>
    -   <L=2R#5>AppleScript</L>
